  <!--
    Least-privilege entitlements for the headless operator-syphon helper and the
    Syphon framework it links. The helper only captures a window via
    ScreenCaptureKit (a TCC runtime grant, not an entitlement) and publishes
    frames over Syphon (Mach/IOSurface, no network), so it needs none of the
    Electron app's JIT / unsigned-memory / network / audio entitlements. It is
    still signed with the hardened runtime; library validation passes because the
    framework is re-signed with the same Developer ID team.
